data.name: label_P6.ToolTip
data.value: If POTBot is dry (E6) this is the angle (P6) at which the unit will move to state E7 and start the GPS for time P7. POTBot will continue to check its water status, if it becomes wet the GPS will stop and the video will start for time P1. POTBot will be in state E2. Angle in Degrees (0 is flat, 90 POTBot is standing on its head, camera pointing down).
